Review Text:
I have visited this place and definitely don't have much good to talk about. We visited for lunch and this was the experience:
1. Masala papad was just fried papad with onion, chilli, tomato chopped on top, no taste of any masala, not even lemon.
2. Biryani, which took 40 mins to come to table was terrible tasting, more like chicken pulao than biryani and was definitely not freshly made to order.
3. During the whole 1 hour that we had to spend there, constant fight was going on in kitchen, manager scolding the staff, staff arguing etc that made the whole experience terrible.
4. The service was exceptionally slow, considering the fact that, other than us, just one more seat was occupied.
5. They took 15 mins to get soft drinks, 20 mins to get masala papad and 40 mins for Biryani, each item after we complained of delay.
All in all, food was not worth the wait and restaurant was not worth the experience.
Good taste which we cant expect the taste nd good packing also nd very good taste i was tasted good food after a lot of days tnq to skynezt restaurent
The diversification of food available at this place is what adds up to the place. Overall a mediocre place to dine. Ambience isn't so great but climbs up in terms of food.
Food and bengali sweets are simply awesome. Ambiance, wash places needs to be more clean & hygienic. I saw lots of fly inside the restaurant on first day, which was not there on second day.
A cosy little joint with matching ambience ! Food was very nice - starters amd sizzlers is what we had and both were really good ! Affordable price !
Restuarent is very nice..nice disighn...bee peace...and service is very good...food also soo yummi....i truly come again . give a nice tast to my toungh..
Financial District guys...No More Worries for Birth Day Party(Catering Service) Orders now.. They Serve very nice and taste is too good like Home made food in my function...Thanks SkyNest Team...
Very good place to have food based on your mood. We have options for varieties of cuisines. Quick service provided and the staff are well organized. Must visit!
Good and Must try for food lovers at Hyderabad Tasty  Chinese items. Hygiene  Food is available here. Service is very good. Keep it up and All the Best.
Best Chinese food I ever had..really impressed. Ambience is good. Nice service staffs. Good spread in food options. I will visit again. .must try..

Awesome Bengali sweets.. rosgollas are must have....try it out.
Gr8 biriyani and chicken roll & kebabs... Nice and cosy ambience ... Excellent place for dining with family and friends..

Awesome bengali food. Price is also cheap. Great ambience. Myself and three of my friend visited just to try out another new restaurent. We were surprised with the variety of Disesh offered and quality of food.

Very good authentic bengali food...
You can try other snacks as well as main course menu... On top of that the behaviour of restaurent members are very polite.

Went to skynest on my way to friends home. Then I thought to stop by after seeing the mural painting, which brought my attention. Initially I thought to have a sandwich, it was cautsy of service staff who made me to eat Thai green curry. But I must say today in skynest I had best Thai curry ever along with soups and kababs. I will definitely go next time. It's must try..

Excellent food and ambience. Soups are extraordianary .
Kebabs are best. Service staff are very polite and humble
Will visit again for sure .

We tried the chicken dishes for the first time last night and the food was great, freshly cooked very tasty and well presented. The waiters were attentive and service overall was good. The restaurant seems to be opened newly . Overall a good meal and great value we will certainly be going back.
Very nice place to have authentic Bengali/odia delicacy. Awesome taste and reasonable prices. Well behaved staff and good ambience. Must try for food lovers at Hyderabad
Very nice place with tasty food. A must try for Chinese items and sweets... Must visit. I enjoyed the food, service, ambience. Truly a place to visit and worth revisiting

No need to look beyond if you have a taste bud for authentic and tasty cuisines along with proper hygiene. One of the very few places in Hyderabad where even a typical nonvegeterian like me is willing to go for a vegetarian dish. Hara Bhara Kabab is one of the must tries.
A highly recommended place if you are looking for some great food and service in an around the Cyberabad corridor.
Great going. Great food and ambience. Lot of options on the menu and homely taste as well. Authentic odia style taste experience as well. Must try cuisines.

Amazing variety of sweets... khoya and cheese based sweets are not common in Hyderabad but Skynest will spoil you with choices...even the regular menu items will give you warmth and comfort of home food

It's a very nice place to visit with family and friends. The service is awesome and taste is very good. The staff is very friendly and the food quality is good.It has a nice ambience and is pocket friendly. It's a must place for people who like to hog over food.

I have been to skynest a couple of times now. Cosy ambience and polite staff. The best part is quality of food - freshly prepared with very high quality ingredients. The pricing is pocket friendly. Certainly a place for 5 star food at 0.5 star rates.

This place is a "must try". Lavish spread of Indian, Chinese, Continental n Thai with some delectable sweet offerings does your tastebuds a world of good. Flavoured Rosogollas are a must try with Biriyani and tandoor kebabs. Nice n well behaved staff makes u feel welcome as well. 5* from me and hope to visit them again soon.
Had a nice experience while eating here. The food the served quickly, and was tasty. The staff is very polite and attentive. The place is a must try!
Amazed with food quality and veriety of of food they serve here.. Must try ... Light on to the pocket without compromise food taste and quantity..

Very impressed with the food quality and multiple options they have in menu..Tried Thai green curry., Which was awesome.. Also ordered online today.. I must say fiid packaging for home delivery is one of the best in Hyderabad. Value for money..
Went there on a friend’s recommendation, was expecting good food but my experience was very disappointing. Place was average, food is average, service is pathetic. Quantity served was very less.
